    Klasse
    Beschreibung
    Calculator
    The Calculator class provides a method to calculate shipping costs based on the dimensions and weight of a packet
    CalculatorArea
    The CalculatorArea class provides a graphical user interface for calculating shipping costs based on the dimensions and weight of a package.
    ExplorerArea
    The ExplorerArea class represents the file explorer in the application, displaying the directory structure and allowing file operations such as creating, deleting, and copying files and directories.
    InspectorArea
    The InspectorArea class represents a section of the user interface where details or properties of a selected item can be inspected and modified.
    MessagesArea
    The MessagesArea class represents a section of the user interface that displays a list of messages or logs.
    PackageCalculator
    The PackageCalculator class is the main entry point for the application.
    Packet
    The Packet class represents a package with specific dimensions (length and height) and weight
    ProjectHandling
    The ProjectHandling class provides methods to handle project operations such as opening projects and creating new files.
    StatusArea
    The StatusArea class represents a section of the user interface where the current status of the application is displayed.
    ToolbarArea
    The ToolbarArea class represents the toolbar of the application, containing various buttons that allow the user to perform key actions such as opening projects, creating new files, saving files, accessing settings, and getting info.
